/* [wxMaxima: comment start ]
Input for the no_stray_children test: it draws a plot so that Maxima
launches a gnuplot process, then the test verifies that neither that
gnuplot nor Maxima itself outlive the wxMaxima batch run. Rendering to a
png file (rather than a window) keeps this working on a headless runner.
   [wxMaxima: comment end   ] */
/* [wxMaxima: input   start ] */
draw2d(terminal=png, file_name="stray_process_check_plot",
       explicit(sin(x),x,-5,5))$
